('3213', '78230_2025-04-03T00:01:21.000Z_156', '78230', '89659c043c30d598', 'PLAZA KOKAI', 'kokai', 'Anders', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Denmark', NULL, 'Couple', NULL, 'Cheap but not worth it', 'Prices reasonably', 'We arrived 30 minutes before check in and asked if we could check in before time. The answer was no, which was okay. 30 minutes later we tried to check in again but the staff full-on ignored us even though we stood right at the lobby desk! they kept asking for \"five more minutes\" which we kept providing. The two hotel staff kept arguing (loudly) with eachother and it did not seem work related. Long story short, we were kept waiting for almost an hour before we got to check-in. 

Now -to the room. First of all: the smell. It is really hard to describe and i am sitting here contemplating how many years of my life i took off by breathing in this room for 3 nights. It was horrible. It smelled like a moldy cellar and the smell persisted even though we had our window open at all time. Also the drain in the bathroom smelled. 

During our stay both the safe did not work (which to be fair they fixed) and one of our lightbulbs kept turning on by itself, which strengthened my belief that this room must have been haunted. 

Oh also - our room card did not work. We had to go down to the lobby and make them renew/update it every. single. time. we. locked. our. door. What is the point of a key card, if it does not work?

The pool is not like you see in the pictures. And the sun is non-existing by the pool just fyi.', '1.0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-03', '2025-02-22', '2025-02-25', 'Hi Anders, we&#39;re truly sorry to hear about your experience. We apologize for the inconvenience you faced during check-in and for the issues in your room. Your feedback is valuable to us, and we will address these concerns to improve. We hope you can give us another chance to provide you with a better stay in the future.', NULL, 'Twin Room', '3', 'en', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-08-03 10:52:06', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/mx/plaza-kokai.es.html', NULL, '0', '13', 'booking', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'completed'),
